Package: scala
Type: Package
Title: Scaled Catch at length and Age Compositions
Version: 0.1
Author: Alistair Dunn [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Alistair Dunn <alistair.dunn@OceanEnvironmental.co.nz>
Description: Scaled Catch at length and Age Compositions (scala) is an  implementation for calculating scaled length compositions from fisheries sampling data, supporting sex-based analysis and bootstrap uncertainty estimation. 
